Cell["4. N consecutive bends: scaling of S(N)", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"057fecff-a374-41a4-bf5b-dc9cab50118e"],

Cell["\<\
Push further: N consecutive 90\[Degree] left bends, total rotation N\[Pi]/2. \
Run the optimiser for N = 1, 2, 3, 4 and see what the maximum area does.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"2ce8aed8-21a1-4dfe-8139-9457ab15f58c"],

