    {
     PaneBox[
      StyleBox["\<\"Figure 6. Left: the Gerver-class shape from the original \
post (non-convex, area 2.22). Right: the best convex sofa the optimiser found \
in this run, area 0.81. The cubic-spline corner trajectory can't quite \
reproduce the half-disc's rigid \\\"slide-rotate-slide\\\" motion; a \
dedicated convex parameterisation would close the gap to \[Pi]/2.\"\>",
       StripOnInput->False,
       FontFamily->"Helvetica",
       FontSize->10,
       FontSlant->Italic],
      Alignment->Center,
